            <p>If you've been whitelisted, you will always receive the latest version from the Google Play Store.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div class="social-links" style="justify-content: center;">
                <a href="https://www.threads.net/@tripperist" target="_blank">Threads</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/tripperist" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
